    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic balance of performance and meticulous upkeep. The exterior paint retains a brilliant luster, showing only the lightest evidence of careful road use, while the body panels remain straight and free of significant blemishes. Inside, the cabin is a testament to careful ownership; the upholstery is clean and firm, the carpets have been protected by floor mats since day one, and the interior retains a fresh, neutral scent. All technological features, including the navigation system and heated seats, are fully operational. Under the hood, the engine runs quietly and delivers power smoothly, backed by a comprehensive folder of service receipts. The suspension feels tight, and the brakes provide confident stopping power. This is a turn-key car that has been maintained to a high standard, perfect for someone who wants a reliable, attractive vehicle without the premium of a brand-new showroom model.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
