      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super reliable for me\u2014it still runs like a dream! It\u2019s clean, well-loved, and totally ready for its next adventure. If you're looking for a dependable car that you can count on, this is the one for you. Feel free to reach out if you want to come take it for a spin!",
      "price": 31500.0,
