      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E46 M3, powered by the high-revving S54 inline-six engine. This example features a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory limited-slip differential. To ensure long-term reliability, the VANOS system has been professionally serviced and the rear subframe reinforced. The suspension retains its factory-spec handling characteristics with refreshed bushings and dampers. While the exterior shows minor cosmetic wear typical of a driven enthusiast vehicle, the powertrain and drivetrain are dialed in for peak performance. A true driver\u2019s car with the valve clearances recently adjusted for optimal induction flow.",
